<main class="bg-slate-50 w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
  <!--Container for contents-->
  <div class="lg:w-3/5 md:w-4/5 pb-10">
    <h1 class="font-bold text-4xl py-10 text-center font-header">Get ready to fly!</h1>  
    <p class="px-5 p-text pb-5 text-center">
    Thank you<%if notice.present?%>, <%= notice %>,<%end%> for requesting a recreational flight with Pitcairn Flight Academy.  We're excited to have you on board and can't wait to share our passion for flying with you.
    A member of our team will be in touch shortly to confirm your flight details. You can also give us a call at <a href="tel:610-495-7000">(610) 495-7000</a> or email us at <a href="mailto:flynow@pitcairnflight.com" class="hover:underline">flynow@pitcairnflight.com</a>
